	<div id="CSD-Training">
		<div>
			<Image
				decoding="async"
				alt="Certified Scrum Developer Scrum Alliance seal"
				src={assets_images_certified_scrum_agile_training_sa_csd_600_png}
			/>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h3><a href="/certified-scrum-developer-csd-training">Certified Scrum Developer (CSD)</a></h3>
			<p>
				The course for developers to do their work more efficiently and with higher levels of
				quality and predictability. Also for Business Analysts, QA, User eXperience, etc who work as
				a part of a bigger team and will benefit from enhanced skills and practice in collaboration.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div>
